      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for the discerning collector, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Maintaining its original showroom luster, the exterior and interior remain in an impeccable, pristine state. Every component has been subjected to rigorous inspection to ensure it meets our highest standards of excellence. This is an uncompromising example of performance and luxury, offering an unparalleled driving experience for those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
