      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive example of the 996.2 widebody aesthetic. This specimen features the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six engine, delivering 320hp with VarioCam Plus timing for a linear power band. The mechanical provenance is exceptional, featuring a documented IMS bearing retrofit, a fresh rear main seal, and a new clutch assembly mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The AWD system utilizes a viscous coupling for seamless torque distribution, while the 'Big Red' four-piston monobloc calipers provide fade-free deceleration. The suspension remains tight with zero bushing deflection, and the underbody is remarkably dry. Finished in Arctic Silver with a flawless interior, this C4S represents a turn-key opportunity for the purist collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
